BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 201.60000000000002 750 Td (WHAT IS ZERO-BASED BUDGETING?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 738 m 552 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (Zero-based budgeting means: INCOME - EXPENSES = $0) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td (Every single dollar has a job. Nothing is left 'floating around') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (without a purpose. This doesn't mean you spend everything -) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (savings and debt payoff ARE jobs for your dollars.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (THE FORMULA:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (Total Income - Total Expenses - Savings - Giving = $0) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (WHY IT WORKS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (- You tell your money where to go instead of wondering where it went) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (- You make spending decisions BEFORE the month, not during) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (- Every dollar is intentional) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (- You catch overspending immediately) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (- You prioritize what matters most) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (HOW TO USE THIS WORKBOOK:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td (1. Calculate your total monthly income) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td (2. List ALL expenses by category) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td (3. Assign dollars to each category until you hit $0) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (4. Track actual spending throughout the month) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (5. Adjust next month based on what you learn) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (RULES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td (- Do the budget BEFORE the month starts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 315 Td (- Both partners must agree \(if applicable\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 299 Td (- Adjust mid-month if needed \(life happens\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 283 Td (- The goal is progress, not perfection) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
